"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月12-13日，由凤凰网主办，凤凰网财经承办的“2021凤凰网财经峰会”在上海举办。复旦大学泛海国际金融学院执行院长、金融学教授钱军在现场分享了当下金融的风险和机遇。谈到[虚拟货币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)时，他表示以[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)为代表的虚拟币不是黄金，不是主流资产，更不是规避通胀风险的最好资产。\",\"timestamp\":1639483097,\"title\":\"复旦大学钱军：比特币不是黄金,不是规避通胀风险的最好资产\"},\"digest\":\"zYGscwvKoGo07LfSdmxG9UZCnA6Rw21lqmujp1Pxsx0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x477CeE414CBbF586922CBD78c1071ac639696AE4\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"i8ZizleOVCHi2oJ1jsp5r1xzCXwFtBF03BKgCO0LpRc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"X7QRqBWFr6FseVSVbKSpf2-oehnyLuPRYey6tg9eKKE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"k0Vi9h6DH1Z8UT3KFqpAyvqmmCCaLz82mC8hZd0xk1l3qOlR_JvCJoins0fmfQlMWGGl4LeZvg7RPFgNu_fEQA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x2d790b7282fac8f574ab864ed4c00208fa51d32701d3b89e99b81ef5779b9a454fc2b6936f81fea042e6d3f5232cff2a9b8e0ef8cbdfccd060108b2209cd997f1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"i8ZizleOVCHi2oJ1jsp5r1xzCXwFtBF03BKgCO0LpRc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"X7QRqBWFr6FseVSVbKSpf2-oehnyLuPRYey6tg9eKKE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"zYGscwvKoGo07LfSdmxG9UZCnA6Rw21lqmujp1Pxsx0\"}"